
arabic-news.txt.gz is an Arabic corpus contains a mixture of formal and spoken (dialectal) Arabic.

It is collected and processed from 5 different sources.


1. Quran text, http://tanzil.net (we used the simple-text version)
2. Watan-2004, (Abbas et al., 2011), https://sites.google.com/site/mouradabbas9/corpora
3. CNN-arabic, (Saad and Ashour, 2010) OSAC: Open Source Arabic Corpus
4. BBC-arabic, (Saad and Ashour, 2010) OSAC: Open Source Arabic Corpus
5. Arabic Book Reviews, (Aly and  Atiya, 2013) LABR: Large Scale Arabic Book Reviews, http://www.mohamedaly.info/datasets/labr


file size: 181MB

---------------------------
source		word count
---------------------------
Quran		751,291
watan-2004	106,289,288
cnn-arabic	23,984,550
bbc-arabic	19,833,141
book-reviews	38,065,922
===========================
TOTOAL:		188,924,192 words
	


